  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the <strong>casual motorsport management</strong> game of the year!<br><br>Experience motorsport like never before: <i>very simple</i>. In this exciting, fast-paced management game you can be team principal of your own team, <strong>upgrade</strong> your car with newly built parts and <strong>sign new drivers</strong> to compete in races and win the championship. Use your drivers <strong>special abilities</strong> to gain an advantage over other drivers on track and leave them in the dust.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build <strong>randomly generated car parts</strong> that suit your purpose! </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459820/extras/d062500127d3653e9f77c7bb3b34b938.poster.avif?t=1737212537\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459820/extras/d062500127d3653e9f77c7bb3b34b938.webm?t=1737212537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459820/extras/d062500127d3653e9f77c7bb3b34b938.mp4?t=1737212537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Customize</strong> your car for each race! </li><li>Handle <strong>fun encounters</strong>off-track! </li><li><strong>Special abilities</strong> and strategy decisions, all in <strong>your hand</strong>!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459820/extras/2a2b9d48ba9ada9c119f3a26c18863d2.poster.avif?t=1737212537\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459820/extras/2a2b9d48ba9ada9c119f3a26c18863d2.webm?t=1737212537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459820/extras/2a2b9d48ba9ada9c119f3a26c18863d2.mp4?t=1737212537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>See you on track!</strong>",
